These are Puzzles for 2x5 Level 9

.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-9-1::.
City: paris, edinburgh, rome, london, new-york
There 5 different types of food: peas, kale, pepper, kiwi, artichoke
 1. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person eating peas##1
 2. the person eating artichoke is somewhere between the person eating kale and the person traveling to rome##7
 3. the person traveling to paris and the person eating artichoke have the same parity positions##9
 4. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to london##5
 5. the person eating kiwi is somewhere to the right of the person eating peas##5
 6. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere to the left of the person eating pepper##5
 7. the person eating artichoke is between the person eating peas and the person eating pepper##2
 8. the person traveling to edinburgh is not the person eating kiwi##6
 9. the person traveling to new-york is on the far left or far right##3
10. the person eating artichoke is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to london##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3      |   4    |      5       |
| Pet     | edinburgh | london     | paris        | rome  | new-york          |
| Sport   | kale  | peas | artichoke | pepper | kiwi |

