.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-9-2::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: iris, sunflower, begonia, dahlia, tulip
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: soccer, basketball, water-polo, biathlon, tennis
 1. the person who's sport is basketball is in an odd position##4
 2. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere between the person who growsbegonia and the person who's sport is biathlon##7
 3. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left or right of the person who's sport is tennis##3
 4. the person who's sport is water-polo is somewhere between the person who growsbegonia and the person who's sport is biathlon##7
 5. the person who growsiris is the person who's sport is soccer##1
 6. the person who growssunflower is in the middle##1
 7. the person who growstulip is on the left or right of the person who's sport is basketball##3
 8. the person who growsiris and the person who's sport is basketball have different parity positions##9
 9. the person who growsiris and the person who's sport is water-polo have different parity positions##9
10. the person who's sport is soccer is not to the right of the person who growsiris##8
11. the person who's sport is water-polo is not to the right of the person who growsdahlia##8

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |    3    |    4     |     5      |
| Food    | begonia  | iris | sunflower  | tulip | dahlia     |
| Hobby   | tennis | soccer   | water-polo | biathlon  | basketball |

