.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-9-3::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, bolivar, baccarat, oliveros, blend
The people use 5 different means of transport: jet-ski, bus, airplane, tram, roller
 1. the baccarat-smoker is not to the left of the person driving the bus##8
 2. the person driving the jet-ski and the blend-smoker have different parity positions##9
 3. the baccarat-smoker is not the person driving the jet-ski##6
 4. the person driving the tram is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 5. the blend-smoker is somewhere to the left of the oliveros-smoker##5
 6. the person driving the tram is somewhere to the left of the person driving the roller##5
 7. the oliveros-smoker is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
 8. the baccarat-smoker is somewhere to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##5
 9. the bolivar-smoker and the person driving the roller have different parity positions##9
10. the person driving the bus is somewhere between the person driving the roller and the oliveros-smoker##7
11. the person driving the bus is somewhere to the right of the person driving the jet-ski##5
12. the person driving the tram is on the left of the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |     2     |    3     |       4       |       5        |
| Beverage   | blend     | oliveros     | baccarat | bolivar | game          |
| Job        | airplane | jet-ski | bus | tram         | roller |

