.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-9-4::.
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: martial-arts, disaster, fantasy, comedy, time-travel
City: boston, marseilles, edinburgh, liverpool, london
 1. the person watching disaster movies is not to the left of the person traveling to boston##8
 2. the person traveling to london is not to the left of the person watching disaster movies##8
 3. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching disaster movies##5
 4. the person watching time-travel movies is somewhere between the person watching comedy movies and the person traveling to edinburgh##7
 5. the person traveling to boston and the person watching fantasy movies have different parity positions##9
 6. the person traveling to marseilles is not to the left of the person watching time-travel movies##8
 7. the person traveling to boston is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##5
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the left of the person watching fantasy movies##8
 9. the person watching disaster movies is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to marseilles##5
10. the person traveling to liverpool is not to the left of the person watching comedy movies##8
11. the person watching martial-arts movies is not to the left of the person traveling to boston##8
12. the person watching disaster movies is in the middle##1
13. the person traveling to london is in the middle##1
14. the person watching fantasy movies is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to boston##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |  2   |    3     |     4      |    5     |
| Beverage   | fantasy    | martial-arts  | disaster | time-travel        | comedy |
| Pet        | edinburgh | boston | london    | marseilles | liverpool      |

