 3. the person eating peach and the person who likes red have different parity positions##9
 4. the person who likes green is in the middle##1
 5. the person who likes red is on the left of the person eating eggplant##1
 6. the person who likes brown is on the left of the person eating peach##1
 7. the person who likes light-blue is on the left or right of the person who likes red##3
 8. the person who likes red is somewhere to the right of the person eating peach##5
 9. the person eating eggplant is not the person who likes red##6
10. the person who likes brown is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
11. the person eating cauliflower is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |   2    |    3     |      4      |   5   |
