.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-9-7::.
5 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, pony, dog, goldfish, chinchilla
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: d&b, house, soul, rock, hip-hop
 1. the fan hip-hop and the owner of the dog have different parity positions##9
 2. the fan rock is somewhere to the left of the fan hip-hop##5
 3. the fan d&b is not to the left of the fan rock##8
 4. the fan hip-hop is somewhere to the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##5
 5. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the owner of the chinchilla##5
 6. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left or right of the fan house##3
 7. the owner of the pony is not to the left of the fan house##8
 8. the fan d&b and the owner of the guinea-pig have the same parity positions##9
 9. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
10. the fan hip-hop is in an odd position##4
11. the fan house is between the owner of the chinchilla and the owner of the pony##2
12. the owner of the pony and the fan house have different parity positions##9

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3      |    4     |     5     |
| Nationality   | chinchilla       | goldfish  | pony  | dog   | guinea-pig   |
| Sport         | rock | house | hip-hop | soul | d&b |

