.:: Puzzle 2x5-Level-9-20::.
There are 5 different favourite colors: amber, red, turquise, apricot, grey
5 different pets are kept: goldfish, goat, lizard, hedgehog, snake
 1. the owner of the hedgehog is not to the right of the owner of the snake##8
 2. the owner of the snake is between the owner of the goldfish and the owner of the hedgehog##2
 3. the owner of the lizard is somewhere to the left of the person who likes grey##5
 4. the owner of the lizard and the person who likes grey have the same parity positions##9
 5. the owner of the goldfish is not to the right of the person who likes grey##8
 6. the person who likes apricot is somewhere to the right of the person who likes red##5
 7. the owner of the lizard is the person who likes red##1
 8. the owner of the goldfish is not to the right of the person who likes turquise##8
 9. the person who likes turquise is somewhere to the right of the owner of the snake##5
10. the person who likes grey is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
11. the person who likes amber is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2     |      3      |      4      |      5      |
| Food    | red    | apricot   | amber     | turquise      | grey   |
| Hobby   | lizard | hedgehog | snake | goldfish | goat |

 